{"tid":1703213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果聽日成功 將會有大量燥底廢中廢老 請唔好同佢地衝突","createTime":"2019-11-10T07:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:45:23.000Z","uid":46330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"beb46639934b60c3d37514aa00a88e6220044f41","tid":1703213,"uid":46330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"8月5日既經驗<br />\n番唔到工既廢老會好撚燥底 而且係大量<br />\n會周圍搵人黎屌/打<br />\n但我地自己人就分散哂做野<br />\n請大家唔好同佢地衝突<br />\n另外 會諗住去黨鐵站舉罷工牌既手足都唔好咁做了"},{"pid":"cdc64745d8bb33e8892e40f2ed679e543e6ce245","tid":1703213,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"咁俾人打 洗唔洗還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0f939f6d523257b92ca4bead2ae751ea0a2cb7","tid":1703213,"uid":46330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cdc64745d8bb33e8892e40f2ed679e543e6ce245","tid":1703213,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"咁俾人打 洗唔洗還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"如果你比廢老打 對面只係一兩個 咁緊係還拖<br />\n但8月5果陣係講十幾廿個打一兩個<br />\n你仲點還拖? 緊係跑啦"},{"pid":"8ac1b45a52dbc1d2962ae3e106e40784e37facd9","tid":1703213,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母<br />\n阻9交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出泥<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n-<br />\n雙十一，周圍塞，阻塞交通變相全民罷工 悼念完一定要有行動，手足既血不可白流<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}